Package: halos-halpi-desktop-branding
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         rpd-common
Provides: halos-desktop-wallpaper
Conflicts: halos-desktop-wallpaper
Replaces: halos-desktop-wallpaper
Description: HALPI2 branded default desktop wallpaper
 This package provides the HALPI2-branded default desktop wallpaper for
 HaLOS HALPI2 desktop variants, overriding the upstream Raspberry Pi OS
 default (shipped via the rpd-common package) using dpkg-divert on the
 pcmanfm system-wide desktop-items conffiles. Per-user wallpaper choices
 take precedence over this default.
 .
 Exclusivity with the generic HaLOS branding (halos-desktop-branding) is
 enforced via the virtual package halos-desktop-wallpaper: only one
 provider can be installed at a time. Pi-gen pre-installs this package on
 HALPI2 desktop builds so the HALPI2-specific artwork wins over the
 generic default.
